  "detailed_description": "Welcome to the fantasy world of <strong>Dalderia</strong>, a land threatened by the <strong>Lich King</strong>. You must defend your nation, the <strong>Crimson Kingdom</strong>. Hack and slash your way through the hordes of the Lich's army to protect your kingdom!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2263330/extras/28cd7852f15996bd431d27d956b8811d.poster.avif?t=1683230450\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2263330/extras/28cd7852f15996bd431d27d956b8811d.webm?t=1683230450\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2263330/extras/28cd7852f15996bd431d27d956b8811d.mp4?t=1683230450\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Collect gold coins to heal and upgrade your sword!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2263330/extras/69b0febd2548cb7461c75ecb00ec81e1.poster.avif?t=1683230450\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2263330/extras/69b0febd2548cb7461c75ecb00ec81e1.webm?t=1683230450\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2263330/extras/69b0febd2548cb7461c75ecb00ec81e1.mp4?t=1683230450\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>And showdown against the Lich King!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2263330/extras/28913fa65d0cea326abec63c71c7bd20.poster.avif?t=1683230450\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2263330/extras/28913fa65d0cea326abec63c71c7bd20.webm?t=1683230450\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2263330/extras/28913fa65d0cea326abec63c71c7bd20.mp4?t=1683230450\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >This Game Features:</h2>Left/Right Movement, Attacking, and Dodge Rolling<br><br>Three enemies with differentiated movesets<br>One boss with three different attacks<br>A shopkeep with upgrades for health and sword damage<br>Up to 7+ rooms to choose from<br>3 soundtracks to listen to<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About My Journey:</h2>Creating this game was actually a year-long project for a high school class. It's my first fleshed-out and public video game, so I hope you all enjoy it!",
  "about_the_game": "Welcome to the fantasy world of <strong>Dalderia</strong>, a land threatened by the <strong>Lich King</strong>. You must defend your nation, the <strong>Crimson Kingdom</strong>. Hack and slash your way through the hordes of the Lich's army to protect your kingdom!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2263330/extras/28cd7852f15996bd431d27d956b8811d.poster.avif?t=1683230450\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2263330/extras/28cd7852f15996bd431d27d956b8811d.webm?t=1683230450\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2263330/extras/28cd7852f15996bd431d27d956b8811d.mp4?t=1683230450\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Collect gold coins to heal and upgrade your sword!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2263330/extras/69b0febd2548cb7461c75ecb00ec81e1.poster.avif?t=1683230450\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2263330/extras/69b0febd2548cb7461c75ecb00ec81e1.webm?t=1683230450\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2263330/extras/69b0febd2548cb7461c75ecb00ec81e1.mp4?t=1683230450\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>And showdown against the Lich King!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2263330/extras/28913fa65d0cea326abec63c71c7bd20.poster.avif?t=1683230450\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2263330/extras/28913fa65d0cea326abec63c71c7bd20.webm?t=1683230450\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2263330/extras/28913fa65d0cea326abec63c71c7bd20.mp4?t=1683230450\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >This Game Features:</h2>Left/Right Movement, Attacking, and Dodge Rolling<br><br>Three enemies with differentiated movesets<br>One boss with three different attacks<br>A shopkeep with upgrades for health and sword damage<br>Up to 7+ rooms to choose from<br>3 soundtracks to listen to<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About My Journey:</h2>Creating this game was actually a year-long project for a high school class. It's my first fleshed-out and public video game, so I hope you all enjoy it!",
